  "title": "Temporary Telemarketer (2 months) - suntec #HMS",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will conduct outreach calls to corporate and individual clients to arrange business meetings, maintain accurate records of contacts, and identify potential leads using online resources during the contract period from 2 Feb 2026 to 24 Apr 2026.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Make calls to corporate and individual clients to secure business meetings</li><li>Record and maintain detailed information of prospects contacted for follow-up and reporting</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><p>Contract duration: 2 Feb 2026 to 24 Apr 2026<br />Working hours: 8.30am to 5.30pm, Monday to Friday<br />Hourly rate: S$12 per hour<br /><br />Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan<br />Jocelyn Chan | Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)<br />Company EA Licence number: 99C4599<br />Personnel EA License: R1331820</p>",
